Install:
=====================================================
1) It's a plugin: 
     clone/extract to APP/plugins/twig_view

2) Make APP/plugins/twig_view/tmp/views writeable

3) Edit your app_controller.php
     var $view = 'TwigView.Twig'

4) Create your views with .tpl or .ctp extension


